questions.question:
(a) Draw a flow graph for the following code segment and calculate its Cyclomatic Complexity:

if (A || B) {
    if (C && D) {
        X = 1;
    } else {
        X = 2;
    }
} else {
    X = 3;
}
Print X;

(b) A software system has 50,000 lines of code and 250 reported defects during testing. Calculate the defect density. (c) Explain how quality metrics are used in practical software development. Discuss at least three practical applications.
